D. J. Williams (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/D._J._Williams_(actor) 0 David John Williams (1868–1949) was a British actor. He also directed one film, The Shuttle of Life, which starred Evelyn Brent. He was born in Ruthin, North Wales and died in Bushey, Hertfordshire. Williams was the nephew of the Anglo-German artist Hubert von Herkomer. David_John_Williams ( 1868 – 1949 ) was a_British_actor .
